            <h2 class="section-title">Database</h2>
            <div class="section-content">
                <p>Each account gets 3 free tables. Consider upgrading to a better plan if you need more tables.</p>
                <p>When creating a table, you can add as many columns as you want.</p>
                <p>Column names and table names are mandatory.</p>
                <p>Each table must have exactly one primary key.</p>
                <p>Primary keys automatically include unique and not empty options.</p>
                <p>Other columns can use auto increment and not empty options.</p>
                <p>You can insert data into tables, and clicking on each row allows for updates and deletions.</p>
                <p>Auto-incrementing columns will automatically increase in value and cannot be modified.</p>
                <p>Tables can be deleted using the drop table button.</p>
            </div>
        </section>

