                <p>Activation toggle switches are located on each endpoint page.</p>
                <p>Each endpoint page contains instructions for both REST API and DML Query methods. Please refer to these when making requests.</p>
                <p>Requests require both an API Key and UID, which can be found on the Endpoints page.</p>
                <p>Insert the UID in the URL and include the API Key in the HTTP request header (key:API Key).</p>
                <p>Requests will be rejected if either is missing.</p>
            </div>
        </section>

